<paragraph id="3519A950254D3071C92ADF54BA05633D" pageId="10" pageNumber="75">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="28204F5D07E1A8488010A2CB69FA60C9" pageId="10" pageNumber="75">Greece, Turkey (Fig. 4).</paragraph>
<caption id="7FBA8CC1824665E9170973DC77505F4E" pageId="10" pageNumber="75">
<paragraph id="D98B9664012A841FD4346445A18B9D84" pageId="10" pageNumber="75">
Figure 4. Distribution map of 
<taxonomicName id="C6FF1B77363546C77A23ECA51026F4AB" class="Insecta" family="Ortheziidae" genus="Ortheziola" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ortheziola" order="Hemiptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="75" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Ortheziola</taxonomicName>
